    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.css"><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>  水在我舌头上<br>  酸口水黏着硬颚</p><p>  味蕾在抗拒<br>  干煸的嘴唇<br>  左右<br>  瓶口亲吻我<br>  紧握瓶身的手</p><p>  正在哭泣又像<br>  流汗着<br>  黏糊<br>  在它的身上</p><p>  排斥着身体，它避免痛苦<br>  背部抗拒挤压——松开了，咸淡的水在面上铺满</p>]]></content>
    
    
