    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.css"><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="伊州令·乙戌记夜">伊州令·乙戌记夜</h2><p>  长风未到今时候。西北天狼狩。残照垣墙留絮因，又总是、倾杯好酒。<br>  难安愁字依旧。吃醉刘伶否？一翻雨雪到心头，命疏与、单薄自我。</p><div class="note success flat"><p>作者自注：我-出韵；中华新韵</p></div>]]></content>
    
    
